headline.main: French Presidential Candidate Fillon's Wife Says He Should Battle On
headline.print_headline: French Presidential Candidate Fillon's Wife Says He Should Battle On

lead_paragraph: World indoor pole vault record holder Jenn Suhr withdrew from the U.S. championships on Saturday, saying she was frustrated with how American title meets are conducted.
